{"tid":94294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆連登鬥慘比賽","createTime":"2017-01-25T06:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T19:47:57.000Z","uid":3066,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12d1ae9baac31e8a6fc41857e1c5b3a5ddd80978","tid":94294,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉 我先<br />\n<br />\n身上得40蚊 但要去親戚屋企拎野<br />\n諗住上完佢屋企拎完野 就去食野<br />\n就到之前個親戚無啦啦打黎叫我幫佢買m記<br />\n仲要係雞翼餐 成$33<br />\n買完比佢食完 佢唔比返錢我<br />\n我捱左成日餓 照上lecture<br />\n個肚餓到咕咕聲 個同學問我「未食野咩？」<br />\n我笑住同佢講 上完就食<br />\n之後因為無錢 得返身上果$7<br />\n用$6搭車返屋企食風"},{"pid":"1c34209cbacde6944f4d0178386a5b9ecd349060","tid":94294,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"ad9ac50483ef0b83d8da96f0cbddb65050f61ab2","tid":94294,"uid":74191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"柯屎無紙巾"},{"pid":"7e2c64e567c03d5a92aab1134690fb0797b915c0","tid":94294,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柯屎無紙巾</blockquote><br />\n拎底褲"},{"pid":"0781fb13194f9f32f3cddd4e12ed79449a2a48e9","tid":94294,"uid":57303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"冚家剷"},{"pid":"df80121b61720226c21793a4157cb13b1f2ab197","tid":94294,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冚家剷</blockquote><br />\n小強，你無事啊嘛小強?"},{"pid":"5345ef02305889af9d65a2c0567d9301fb045b4b","tid":94294,"uid":79262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"之前沖沖下涼突然停水，但係已經茶曬沐浴露同洗頭水，等到有返水，已經係3粒鐘之後嘅事"},{"pid":"8285b48147302912fd28cc7a3d37d002849d38a7","tid":94294,"uid":11461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:29:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a1fa85b6e32aaa8835d94cb4f6e31d9501ebbd7","tid":94294,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc